# Zero Trust Security Infrastructure Configuration

This directory contains Terraform templates for Cloudflare Zero Trust security deployment.

## Components

- `main.tf` - Zero Trust configuration
- `policies/` - Access control policies
- `rules/` - Security rules and filters
- `identity/` - Identity provider integration
- `device/` - Device certification policies

## Features

- Identity provider integration
- Device certification
- Access policies by application
- Network-level security
- Application-level security
- Audit logging
